==Daily==
===Hey, (Trailblazer)===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Luocha:''' Hey, (Trailblazer)
:'''Luocha:''' Sorry to disturb you, but there's something I forgot to ask
:'''Luocha:''' Like I said before, the journey of a traveling merchant is mostly drawn-out and boring
:'''Luocha:''' Do you have any advice for passing time when traveling, (Trailblazer)?
:{Choice} Chat with people
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Chat with the people around you
::'''Luocha:''' To be honest, I'm not great at opening a conversation... But with that coffin around me, a conversation is bound to happen
:{Choice} Do whatever you like
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Do whatever pleases you. Play games, read books, watch the scenery, anything you want
::'''Luocha:''' Finish the books I've borrowed on the Luofu, this might not be a bad idea
:{Choice} Sleep the whole way
::'''(Trailblazer):''' There's really nothing to do on the road except sleeping
::'''Luocha:''' The purpose is the end point, not the process, huh?
:'''Luocha:''' Is that what you've been doing in your journeys, (Trailblazer)?
:{Choice} Of course
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Of course, that's what I do all the time
::'''Luocha:''' Sounds like you've got some insights
::'''Luocha:''' Thank you for giving me a sincere suggestion
:{Choice} Of course not
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Of course not, I never do that
::'''Luocha:''' Sounds like you chose something that you think suits me best
:'''Luocha:''' I'll try it
}}
