===(Trailblazer), when you came...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Luocha:''' (Trailblazer), when you came to the Luofu, where did you stay? How was it?
:'''Luocha:''' Wait, lemme guess
:'''Luocha:''' Petrichor Inn?
:{Choice} It's not bad
::'''(Trailblazer):''' That's right, I did stay at the Petrichor Inn
::'''(Trailblazer):''' A premium suite, it's not bad
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 06.png|80px|&lbrack;Thumbs Up&rbrack;]]
::'''Luocha:''' The premium suite is not easy to book, most people would just go there for the Starwatcher Avenue's night view
:{Choice} It's so-so
::'''(Trailblazer):''' That's right, I did stay at the Petrichor Inn
::'''(Trailblazer):''' But honestly, it's nothing to write home about
::'''(Trailblazer):''' After all, every time I stay in a hotel, I worry about bad things happening, so I've got no time to think about other stuff
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 02.png|80px|&lbrack;cry&rbrack;]]
::'''Luocha:''' Sounds like you've been through some rough patch
:'''Luocha:''' I stay at the Petrichor Inn often. After all, it's easy to get anywhere from there
:'''Luocha:''' As a traveling merchant, I don't indulge much in my trips, but even so, I get bored after a while
:'''Luocha:''' There are some units in the Skyward Pavilions neighborhood that allow short-term rentals, so I went there
:'''Luocha:''' That's where Xianzhou residents usually stay
:{Choice} Sounds like you are being watched.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sounds like it's not that convenient and that you are being watched somehow.
::'''Luocha:''' That depends on how you see it
::'''Luocha:''' Life on the Xianzhou is not that shut-in. People are friendly, so experiencing and observing their way of life is my hobby...
::'''Luocha:''' But that's not quite right. Most of the time, I'm the one being observed.
:{Choice} So, you're like a Xianzhou resident now?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Looks like you've become a Xianzhou resident yourself now
::'''Luocha:''' Heh heh, you know me
::'''Luocha:''' Yeah, with that, I've blended with the populace on the Luofu
:'''Luocha:''' I'm nomadic and have nowhere to call my home. Staying in the Skyward Pavilions neighborhood even for a while helps me forget my identity as a traveling merchant
:'''Luocha:''' So, I quite like it
:{Choice} I'll try too
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I shall try it too, next time
::'''Luocha:''' Alright, maybe we can be neighbors if we're lucky
:{Choice} I probably can't
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I probably can't stay there
::'''Luocha:''' Can I ask the reason?
::{Choice} I'm scared!
:::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm scared!
::{Choice} I'm not used to another bed!
:::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm not used to another bed!
::{Choice} I'm a clean freak!
:::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm a clean freak!
::'''Luocha:''' I see
::'''Luocha:''' I understand, and I respect your decision
::'''Luocha:''' If you change your mind some day, we'll talk
}}
