===(Trailblazer), I couldn't sleep last night===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Luocha:''' (Trailblazer), I couldn't sleep last night
:'''Luocha:''' Maybe I'm too naive. Without returning customers, it's hard to do business at night
:'''Luocha:''' I went to the Aurum Alley, it's an old street famous for its night bazaar
:'''Luocha:''' As a traveling merchant, how can I not check it out?
:{Choice} You were selling?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You were selling?
::'''Luocha:''' Yes and no, buying and selling are always reciprocal that way
::'''Luocha:''' I do have some uncommon trinkets with me, but it's not like I can meet someone who likes them every time
::'''Luocha:''' That being said, people on the Xianzhou are friendly. Even if they don't buy things, they'll still chit-chat with me
:{Choice} You were buying?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You were buying?
::'''Luocha:''' Yes and no, buying and selling are always reciprocal that way
::'''Luocha:''' Many shops do have some interesting thingamabobs with them, but it's not like everything would suit my taste at a given time
::'''Luocha:''' That being said, people on the Xianzhou are friendly. Even if I don't buy things, they'll still chit-chat with me
:'''Luocha:''' I just didn't think the chatting will last until shops start to close up
:'''Luocha:''' I did have a fun night, but thinking back, what exactly did I gain?
:{Choice} You gained intel!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Don't put it like that
::'''(Trailblazer):''' At least you gained hot info of Xianzhou's industries!
::'''Luocha:''' Haha, looks like I'm truly a traveling merchant in your eyes
:{Choice} At least you gained friendship!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Don't put it like that
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You gained the friendship of Xianzhou people!
::'''Luocha:''' That's right, is there anything more precious than that?
:{Choice} You gained eyebags!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Don't put it like that
::'''(Trailblazer):''' At least you got yourself a pair of eye bags!
::'''Luocha:''' A shame, I'm the type of person who doesn't show even if I stayed up all night
:'''Luocha:''' If you have a chance, you should check out the Aurum Alley
:'''Luocha:''' And if I'm still here on Xianzhou, call me along
}}
